Package: CoSIA
Type: Package
Title: An Investigation Across Different Species and Tissues
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anisha Haldar
Maintainer: Anisha Haldar <anishah@uab.edu>
Description: CoSIA provides researchers with the ability to compare across species and tissues using gene expression by providing multiple gene-expression based metrics for calculating and visualizing transcriptome diversity and variation.
